            <p>
                Perfect for families and beginners. Enjoy a relaxing
                journey down scenic rivers with gentle rapids and
                beautiful views.
            </p>
        </article>

        <article class="trip-card">
            <img src="rafting-action.jpeg" alt="White water rapids">

            <h2>Canyon Rapids Expedition</h2>

            <p>
                Experience exciting Class III and IV rapids while
                exploring breathtaking canyon landscapes with
                professional guides.
            </p>
